snippet.title: Kirby's Dream World(Online MMORPG) Emerald locations
snippet.description:
I was board,so I decided to show how to get all the 7 chaos emeralds in Kirby's Dream World,and how to get the Master Emerald Blade,for those who don't know where they are.
BTW:I'm Smashbro on KDW,if you see me I'll try to help you if your stuck(I'm LVL 500)
Note:To get the blue emerald,you have to go through the maze,I only put up some of the hardest parts in the maze so you can know how to get through them.
Also,if you don't know what KDW is,the site is right here: http://kirbysdreamworld.blogspot.com/

the game is a fan-game made by fans,right now not many people are playing,so please join.
BTW:Srry for lag,it does that when I record a vid.
NOTE:I came back to KDW after a long time,I still go by smashbro,but if you see someone named IDK600,thats also me.
